jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.geometry

Class GeometryDatas

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.geometry.GeometryDatas

  • public class GeometryDatas
extends Object
    The class GeometryDatas, which contains following objects which are related to geometry.
    • SBML model Model
    • Geometry Geometry
    • coordinates of boundary
    • dimension
    • list of domains(String)
    • list of SpatialImages
    This class is used in MainSBaseSpatial, to visualize a model in 3D space. Date Created: Jun 25, 2015
    Author:
    Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
